Class SingleExprTraceRefiner<S extends ExprState,A extends ExprAction,P extends Prec,R extends Refutation>

java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.analysis.expr.refinement.SingleExprTraceRefiner<S,A,P,R>
All Implemented Interfaces:
ArgRefiner<S,A,P>, Refiner<P,ARG<S,A>,Trace<S,A>>
public class SingleExprTraceRefiner<S extends ExprState,A extends ExprAction,P extends Prec,R extends Refutation> extends Object implements ArgRefiner<S,A,P>
A Refiner implementation that can refine a single trace (of ExprStates and ExprActions) using an ExprTraceChecker and a PrecRefiner.
